  <entry>
    <title>java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError</title>
    <link href="https://knightofbatons.github.io/2017/01/05/java-lang-NoClassDefFoundError/"/>
    <id>https://knightofbatons.github.io/2017/01/05/java-lang-NoClassDefFoundError/</id>
    <published>2017-01-04T16:01:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-03-09T09:03:49.649Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>Hadoop jar 运行Jar包的时候出现的错误<br><a id="more"></a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>今天照着<a href="http://blog.csdn.net/fxsdbt520/article/details/53893421" target="_blank" rel="external">之前提到过的博客</a>尝试了一下HBASE-&gt;ElasticSearch<br>用到了TableMapper，结果 java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError<br>原因大概是编译的时候有 但运行的时候没找到</p>
<h4 id="错误原因"><a href="#错误原因" class="headerlink" title="错误原因"></a>错误原因</h4><p>hadoop-env.sh<br>classpath设置有问题，导致找不到jar <a href="http://pwg17.github.io/2014/09/24/hadoop-NoClassDefFoundError/" target="_blank" rel="external">这里</a>说的比较清楚</p>
<h4 id="解决方式"><a href="#解决方式" class="headerlink" title="解决方式"></a>解决方式</h4><p>比如我加上Hbase的Jar包<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> f <span class="keyword">in</span> /home/hbase-1.2.4/lib/*.jar; <span class="keyword">do</span></div><div class="line">HADOOP_CLASSPATH=<span class="variable">$&#123;HADOOP_CLASSPATH&#125;</span>:<span class="variable">$f</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">done</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>问题解决了</p>
<h3 id="夜空"><a href="#夜空" class="headerlink" title="夜空*"></a>夜空*</h3><p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="https://music.daoapp.io/iframe?song=22691514&qssl=1&qlrc=0&qnarrow=0&autoplay=1"></iframe><br>今天这 HBASE-&gt;ElasticSearch 真像这嗓音一样有毒<br>很多事情都不像最初想的那么简单啊，都快习惯了</p>
]]></content>
    
